        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository bd77de97-e398-47be-a948-a88a3da74aed).Image",
        "Description": "Hello Agent Mooney. Today, we have two clients: An ex-Kronstadt mechanic who quit after insufferable working conditions. He wants us to kill his former boss, Grace Miller. He would prefer her to suffer as badly as he felt and thus will pay extra if handled up close and personal. Our second client is a current engineer working in Kronstadt. He is annoyed that his bosses&apos; bodyguards are taking all the energy drinks in the vending machines. He&apos;s a little squeamish, so make it look like an accident.",
